                                <p>Plants provide us with food through which we get essential nutrients and energy.
                                    It provides us with daily life essentials.
                                    Plants help in cleaning the air so that we can breathe freshly.
                                    They reduce sickness, stress, and anxiety.
                                    We get woods, leaves, and tree branches to use as fuels.</p>
                                <div class="row mb-30">
                                    <div class="col-lg-7">
                                        <p>Plants are multicellular eukaryotes. They have organelles called chloroplasts and cell walls made of cellulose. Plants also have specialized reproductive organs. Almost all plants make food by photosynthesis</p>
