                                        <img src="~/website/img/bg-img/36.jpg" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p>Through the almost magical process of photosynthesis, trees and plants absorb carbon dioxide and release life-giving oxygen, helping to regulate our planet's climate. By planting more trees, we can bolster this natural defence mechanism and help to mitigate the impact of global warming.</p>
                                <blockquote>
