                                        <h5>Richard Jefferies</h5>
                                    </div>
                                </blockquote>
                                <h4>Plant the love of the holy ones within your spirit.</h4>
                                <p>For human use, plants supply many products like firewood, timber, fruits, vegetables, medicines, dyes, pesticides, etc. Plants provide shelters to many living organisms like species of insects, worms, mammals, birds, reptiles.</p>
